Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.81,0:00:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, exactly!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.60,0:00:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh right, Pastel! Remember how you\Nwere acting kinda funny the other day?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.14,0:00:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.74,0:00:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Like climbing onto the train luggage rack \Nor curling up on Light’s lap.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.30,0:00:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.47,0:00:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Also when you ate Ms. Apple's lunch and got totally\Nobsessed with the rhythmic gymnastics ribbon.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.85,0:00:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So you mean when I switched bodies with that cat? {unsure if she says this or it's in her mind}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.06,0:00:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But honestly, I kind of liked that.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:44.70,0:00:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.64,0:00:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know... when you ate \Nall my cookies like they were delicious.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.11,0:00:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.01,0:00:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn’t even use your hands, \Nyou just went at them nonstop!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:56.47,0:00:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Did I, really?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, don’t play dumb, Pastel. \NIt's you I'm talking about!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:03.22,0:01:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:05.39,0:01:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.92,0:01:11.59,Thought,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but that wasn’t me! \NThat was the cat!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:11.59,0:01:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My, how you ate them... so moving!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:15.12,0:01:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:15.70,0:01:22.70,Thought,,0,0,0,,She’s seriously got the wrong idea… this is bad… \Nis this turning into something worse?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:22.70,0:01:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.64,0:01:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:24.36,0:01:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Cookies! {lit: she brought them out}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.66,0:01:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! You scared me!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:27.37,0:01:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, yelling like that... \Nare you {\i1}that{\i0}{\i0\fsp3} {\fsp0}happy?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:31.60,0:01:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:32.26,0:01:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, Pastel, don’t hold back!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.37,0:01:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dig in!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.64,0:01:45.79,Thought,,0,0,0,,Help! WinBee! Mint! Light!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.17,0:01:54.26,Thought,,0,0,0,,W-What a way to go... {lit: is this [the series] really going to end like this }
